Global execution context

1)create a global object
2)create an object called this
3)set up memory space for variables and functions
4)Assign variable declaration default value undefined while placing function declaration in memory.

function execution context
1)create an arguments object
2)create an object called this.
3)Set up memory for variable and function
4)Assign variable declaration default value i.e., undefined while placing function declaration in memory.
---------------------------

closure scope
Whenever there is a inner function then is closure scope which have the access to outer scope variables.

